parameters.query:
INSERT INTO Events (
    event_code, 
    event_name, 
    start_date, 
    stop_date, 
    location_id
) VALUES (
    $1, -- event_code
    $2, -- event_name
    $3, -- start_date
    $4, -- stop_date
    '11440' -- MAQ Location ID
)
ON CONFLICT (event_code) 
DO UPDATE SET
    event_name = $2,
    start_date = $3,
    stop_date = $4;
